summary: This is a confidential lieutenant's log and daily activity log from the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York, dated August 10, 2019. This date is significant as it is the day Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell.

persons.name: Jeffrey Epstein
persons.context: The log is from the correctional center where he was held; his death occurred on this date.

events.title: Jeffrey Epstein's Death
events.description: Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell at the Metropolitan Correctional Center.

locations: Metropolitan Correctional Center, 150 Park Row, New York, NY 10007
keyFacts: The document is a confidential lieutenant's log from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York.
The log is dated August 10, 2019, the day Jeffrey Epstein died in custody.
The document's classification as 'CONFIDENTIAL' and its inclusion in the SDNY Epstein files indicates its relevance to the investigation into his death.
